snippet.title: Cave Digger 2 | Full Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Cave Digger 2 full Release is finally here, yay!
Go on an enigmatic adventure in this 1-4 player VR game set in an alternative western world. Discoveries, dangers and digging await the Prospector.

Get Cave Digger 2 from: 
Steam 👉 https://bit.ly/3GUffnc
App Lab 👉 https://ocul.us/36zTs7u
SideQuest 👉 https://bit.ly/3IPRY66
PlayStation 👉 (11th of September)
⛏️🤠 Check out our Discord for further news  http://discord.gg/cavedigger 

🐦You can also follow us on Twitter https://twitter.com/vr_kiwi
